Before generating the final report:

1. Verify every readable file was processed.
2. Verify every WSTG test case was evaluated.
3. Verify all findings contain evidence.
4. Verify report integrity.
5. Verify all referenced files exist.
6. Verify severity mappings are populated.
7. Generate final scan statistics.

